title: The Drink Champs Interview
description:
Drink Champs bring the ruckus to the No Jumper podcast! Nore and EFN talk about absolutely everything, how they started their media imprint, how the name came about, Nore's relationships with Jay, Nas, Joe Budden, Vince Staples, Dame Dash, Fat Joe, DMX, UGK and more. Plus, Nore gives his stance on Zane Low and Apple Music.
